h2 Create a new user

p  A new user is created for the blog as a superuser, so make sure you do this right.<br>

-if (flash)
  -if (flash.error)
    p.flash.error #{flash.error}
  -if (flash.info)
    p.flash.info #{flash.info}

form(name="user-form",method="post",action="/adduser")
  p  
    label Username:
       input(type="text",name="username", required)
  p  
    label Password:
       input(type="password",name="password", required)
  p  
    input(type="submit",name="submit",value="Submit",onClick="return confirm('Are you sure?');")
